parameters.query:
with userz as (
select distinct u.id
, u.uuid
, concat(u.first_name, ' ', u.last_name) as name 
, u.email
, MIN(case when b.status = 'completed' then b.request_end_at end) as cft_enddate
, AGE(NOW(), MIN(CASE WHEN b.status = 'completed' THEN b.request_end_at END)) as days_after_cft
from users u 
left join listings l on l.user_id = u.id
left join bookings b on b.listing_id = l.id 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
where b.status = 'completed'
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
--and u.id = '5162'
group by 1,2,3,4
--HAVING AGE(NOW(), MIN(CASE WHEN b.status = 'completed' THEN b.request_end_at END)) = INTERVAL '1 month'
)

, details as (
select distinct u.id
, count(distinct case when b.status = 'completed' then b.id end) as completed_bookings
, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN b.status IN ('accepted', 'completed', 'start_driving', 'waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car', 'rejected') THEN b.id END) as  requests
, ROUND((CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN b.status IN ('accepted', 'completed', 'start_driving', 'waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car') THEN b.id END)AS DECIMAL(10, 2)) /
  cast(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN b.status IN ('accepted', 'completed', 'start_driving', 'waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car', 'rejected') THEN b.id end)AS DECIMAL(10, 2)))*100,0) as acceptance
from users u 
left join listings l on l.user_id = u.id
left join bookings b on b.listing_id = l.id 
where u.id in (select id from userz)
group by 1 )

, reviews as ( 
select distinct u.id 
, ROUND(avg(br.rating),1)as avg_review
from users u
left join listings l on l.user_id = u.id
left join bookings b on b.listing_id = l.id
left join booking_reviews br on br.booking_id = b.id
where u.id in (select id from userz)
group by 1
)

select u.id, u.uuid, u.name, u.email, u.cft_enddate, d.completed_bookings, d.requests, d.acceptance, r.avg_review
from userz u 
left join details d on d.id = u.id 
left join reviews r on r.id = u.id
where u.days_after_cft BETWEEN INTERVAL '1 month' and (interval '1 month' + interval '1 day')
